00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:19,180
And if you approach this with the old blueprint model, the intuitive answer seems obvious.

463
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:19,800
Yeah.

464
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:24,620
If the human brain is structurally a skyscraper and the mouse brain is a bungalow, the human

